Pepsi-Cola USA said received anexclusive five-year contract to supply soft drinks to all ofHarcourt Brace Jovanovich Inc's &lt;HBJ> Sea World theme parks inthe United States, effective Jan 1, 1988.    Pepsi said Sea World has had an account with Coca-Cola forthe past 16 years. Pepsi said Sea World operates five majortheme parks in Orlando, San Diego, Cleveland, Winter Haven,Fla., and Baseball City, Fla.    Pepsi said the new agreement also calls for a majorpromotional partnerships between the companies. Reuter&#3;